Module org.example.fitnessprojectgui
Package ProjectFitness

Class MemberList

java.lang.Object
ProjectFitness.MemberList
public class MemberList extends Object
The MemberList class represents a fitness club member. It contains information about the member's profile, membership expiration date, and home studio location.
